subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened national, regional and local level capacity to mainstream gender equality and women’s empowerment in government policies and institutions
subproject.description: The project will facilitate the fight against discrimination against women and to implement and monitor the implementation of the UN Convention for the Elimination of All forms of Discrimination against Women through a multi-sectoral and integrated approach.
subproject.gender code: Gender Equality as a principal objective
subproject.title: Gender Programme
